  {
    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "The issue seems to be introduced as soon as we're using `connectHitInsights`. Because we have server-side rendering, we do it this way:\r\n\r\n```\r\nexport default connectHitInsights(getAlgoliaAnalytics())(CustomHit);\r\n```\r\n\r\n```\r\nexport function getAlgoliaAnalytics() {\r\n    if (isServerSide()) {\r\n        return null;\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    if (isEmpty(window.aa)) {\r\n        return null;\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    return window.aa;\r\n}\r\n```",
    "created_at": "2021-03-09T11:15:22Z",
