  {
    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "I simplified the example and found the following things that matter: https://codesandbox.io/s/stoic-hermann-98bx9?file=/pages/index.js\r\n\r\n1. stateResults *behind* hits has the issue, *before* it doesn't\r\n2. a hitComponent must be given in default Hits component\r\n\r\nFor your specific use case, can you try putting StateResults in front of Hits?",
    "created_at": "2021-03-10T10:19:54Z",
    "html_url": "https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/issues/5255#issuecomment-1363060873",
